Package: sfislands
Type: Package
Title: Makes it easier to build neighbourhood lists
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Kevin Horan
Maintainer: Kevin Horan <kevin.horan.2021@mumail.ie>
Description: It helps construct contiguities when islands are present.
    But also helps with checking and editing contiguities.
    Provides functions for extracting predictions from areal models.
